    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $.validator.addMethod("sfemail", function (value, element) {
                var re = new RegExp("\\w+([-+.]\\w+)*@\\w+([-.]\\w+)*\\.\\w+([-.]\\w+)*", "gi");

                return this.optional(element) || re.test(value);
            }, "A valid email is required.");

            $.validator.addMethod("filesize", function (value, element, param) {
                return this.optional(element) || (element.files[0].size <= ((1024 * param) * 1024));
            }, "Please select a file smaller than {0}MB.");

            $("form").validate({
                submitHandler: function () {
                    var isSkip = $($("form").data("validator").submitButton).hasClass("cancel");

                    return isSkip || $("form").valid();
                }
            });

            $("[email=true][required=true]")
                .rules("add", {
                    sfemail: true
                });

            $("[required=true]")
                .rules("add", {
                    required: true
                });

            $("[type=file]")
                .rules("add", {
                    filesize: 5 // size in MiB
                });

            $.validator.messages.required = "This field is required.";
            $.validator.messages.email = "A valid email is required.";
        });
    </script>
